!! # Greenlandic morphological analyser
! ==========================================================================

! ========================================================================== !
!! Fil for at generere de centrale morfologiske processer i vor grГёnlandske analysator
!========================================================================== !

!! # Multicharacter symbols

Multichar_Symbols

!v2     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Alternativt /v/ i lГҘneord, der ikke skal slettes efter /u/
AA+     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = prГҰfiks
TA+     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = prГҰfiks

!! ## Tags for POS (primary tags)

!! ### Main Word Classes

 +encl   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = clitic to separate clitics from suffixes with identical upper form in disambiguator.cg3 (TTAAQ)
 +N      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Noun
 +V      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Verb
 +Pali   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Particle-like - partikellignende
 +Conj   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Conjunction
 +Adv    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Adverb
 +Interj !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Interjection
 +Pron   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Pronoun
 +Prop   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Propernoun
 +Num    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Numeral
 +Symbol !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = independent symbols in the text stream, like ВЈ, вӮ¬, В©
 +Arab   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = pga- brug i ~/langtech/shared-mul/src/fst/stems/telephone.lexc 



!! ## Secondary tags

!! ### Tags for Verbs

 +Gram/IV !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Intransitive Verb !PL 20180319 ny formalisme gennemfГёrt livm 20180324
 +Gram/TV !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Transitive Verb !PL 20180319 ny formalisme gennemfГёrt livm 20180324
 +Gram/HV !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Non-marked agentive Verb (used as Half-transitive)
 +Gram/Db !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Double-transitive Verb. PL tilfГёjet 20180319
 +Gram/Exclm !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Exclamation !Flyttet fra primГҰre tags 20180420 PL

!! ### Tags for Pronouns

 +Gram/Int    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Interrogative Pronoun
 +Gram/Pers   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Personal Pronoun
 +Gram/Coref  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Reflexive Pronoun
 +Gram/Indef  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Indefinitive Pronoun

!! ### Tags for Other Word Classes

 +Gram/Dem   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Demonstative pronoun, demonstrative adverb or demonstrative interjection
 +Gram/Cong  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Various Pronoun, eg. tamaq, kisi (personkongruensdeklination)
 +Gram/Abbr  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Abbreviation
 +Gram/ACR   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Acronyms
 +Gram/Adj   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Adjektiver optaget direkte inkl. ubГёjet anvendelse fГёr kerne

