!! ### Grammar

 +Gram/Comp  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Composita !SГҰrlig tag til NIQ ajor/saper/artor/nalu- konstruktioner ved transitive verber
 +Gram/Refl  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Reflexive, reciprocal or passive !asavoq
 +Gram/Reci  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Reciprocal !naapipput
 +Gram/Pass  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Passive !used when a derivational morpheme not explicitely denotes a passivisation, or when intransitive flexion changes an active verb into a passive
 +Gram/PlurTant  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = plurale tantum noun: ilaqutariit
 +Gram/SingTant  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = singulare tantum noun: sila
 +Gram/Ord   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Ordinal number !pingajuat
 +Gram/Hyb !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = FГёlger hybriderne for at bestemme stederne hvor strengene kan klippes i to ord ved hybriderne
 +Gram/TransverbNIQ !!= *__@CODE@__ = NIQ-former med transitivt verbale egenskaber. PL20210417
 +Gram/ImpNeg !!=
 +Gram/ImpPos !!= 

 +Gram/lex ! leksikaliseret stamme

!sekundГҰre tags til KATERSAT start
+Gram/-assib
+Gram/-epen !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = ingen epentese ved lГҘneord, sГҘ der kan genereres en. bestemt form til Katersat. batteriip versus batterip. ELLER ved vokaler aa+u -> aaju (nutaanngilaq)
+Gram/-schwa !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = minus schwa, angerlaanngilaa
+Gram/Alt !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Ablative alternative form -minngaanniit/-ninngaanniit. Eller uregelmГҰssig pujoq->puggup 
+Gram/Alt2 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Ablative alternative form 2 -minngarnit/-ninngarnit
+Gram/GAQ !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = TAQ allomorf i formen gaq, for at kunne generere en bestemt form til Katersat, opslag: maligaq -> malikkap, ikke malitap
+Gram/GEM !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = gemineret
+Gram/GEMloan !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = geminering af sidste konsonant i lГҘneord
+Gram/GEMss !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = latent konsonant j gemineret (ergo GEM) som ss, tag brugt til at generere form til Katersat, kikiak -> kikissap (og ikke kikiap, kikiaap)
+Gram/Lo !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Ablative long form -miit/-niit
+Gram/Sh !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Ablative short form -mit/-nit
+Gram/additive !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = den additive form af et suffiks, som bГҘde kan vГҰre additiv og truncativ, SIMA ved t-stammer
+Gram/assib !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = assibileret, for at kunne generere en bestemt form til Katersat
+Gram/epen !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = epentese i ved lГҘneord, der ender pГҘ en konsonant. ELLER ved vokaler aa+u -> aa (nutaajunngilaq) 
+Gram/fus !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = fusionerende, t+l -> s, iggit+LIR -> iggiser
+Gram/inchoative !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = inchoativt suffiks
+Gram/liup !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = trunkativ, stГҰrk bГёjning LIK
+Gram/llip !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = trunkativ, gemination LIK
+Gram/llup !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = final vokal + konsonant trunkering, stГҰrk bГёjning, geminering LIK
+Gram/meta !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = metatese, imeq, ermup
+Gram/regass !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = sidste vokal fjernet, dernГҰst regressiv assimilation, aaveq->aarrit
+Gram/repl !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = replaciv, for at kunne generere replaciv form til Katersat, aappinngilaa framfor aappalinngilaa, nГҘr opslaget er aapperpaa
+Gram/schwa !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = med schwa, angerlaatinngilaa
+Gram/str !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = stГҰrk bГёjning + trunkering, -up for at kunne vГҰlge en bestemt form til Katersat, aagiak -> aagiaap, ikke aagiap
+Gram/strnasal !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = stГҰrk bГёjning, stammefinal k nasaleret
+Gram/truncative !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = den truncative form af et suffiks, som bГҘde kan vГҰre additiv og truncativ, SIMA ved t-stammer
+Gram/wea !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = svag bГёjning, -p

+Orth/longi !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = long i, benziina versus benzina
+Orth/shorti !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = short i, benzina versus benziina  
+Orth/ztos !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = s used instead of z, bensiina
!sekundГҰre tags til KATERSAT slut

!! ### Derivation

 +Der/Vok   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Vocative
 +Der/Unk !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Ukendt morfem !Ukendte morfemer i ellers analyserede stammer for at fГҘ rigtig lemmaanalyse, som orsoq+NNAP+nv+UNK+vn:orsunnattaaq
 +Der/vv    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = verb to verb
 +Der/nn    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = noun to noun
 +Der/nv    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = noun to verb
 +Der/vn    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = verb to noun
 +Der/xx  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Follows the enclitic suffix TUQ to be able to distinguish TUQ+xx from the derivational morpheme TUQ+vn in CG: qanortoq
 +Der/Quote !! Citerede ordformer  jf. Kleinschmidt ^rpoДё

!! ### Dialect
 +Dial/Ngr !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Northern dialect (such as ng for g; predictable dialectal changes might be dealt with in the postprosessor in stead)
 +Dial/Sgr !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Southern dialect (such as VVC for VVCC), aneeqavoq (and not aneeqqavoq)
 +Dial/Egr !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Eastern dialect
 +Dial/Vgr !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Western dialect (such as rng for rn)


!! ### Tags to mark loan word entries with a diverting orthography
!! That is, they need special treatment in e.g. speech syntesis.
 +OLang/DAN  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Danish stem: profet
 +OLang/ENG  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = English stem: game

!! ### Orthograhy
 +Orth/Arch   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Archaic language, (stem, morpheme, flexion, or sandhi): tikisimavoq, asallutigik, agpГў (for anГӯpГў)
 +Orth/Youth   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Youth language: asallutigu
 +Orth/Alt   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Substandard language (hyphens among other thingsвҖҰ): isissavoq, Qaanaaq-mut, fabrikki, poorвҖҷlu
 +Orth/Hyph !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = bindestreg ved lГҘneord, for at kunne generere en bestemt form til Katersat
 +Orth/-Hyph !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = uden bindestreg ved lГҘneord, for at kunne generere en bestemt form til Katersat

!! ### Usage/error
 +Use/-Spell  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Do not include in speller
 +Use/Hybrid  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = For generating split hybrids. Should not be included in speller, analyser, or norm-generator
 +Err/Sub   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Not authorized spelling: 2-imik
 +Err/Orth  !! !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**  tag, vi ikke bruger, men som optrГҰder i de delte filer

!! ## Tags for Inflection

!! ### Numerus
 +Sg !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Singularis
 +Du !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Dualis
 +Pl !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Pluralis

!! ### Kasus
