 +Rel    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Relative
 +Trm    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Terminalis
 +Lok    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Locative
 +Aeq    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Aequalis
 +Ins    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Instrumentalis
 +Via   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Vialis
 +Abl    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Ablative

!! ### SГҰrlige 3./4. persons kasus med DivPron (Gram/Cong)
 +Nom    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Nominative
 +Akk    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Accusative

!! ### Modus
 +Ind       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Indicative
 +Int       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Interrogative
 +Imp       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Imperative
 +Opt       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Optative
 +Cau       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Causative
 +Con       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Conditional
 +Par       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Participium
 +Cont      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Infinitive
 +ContNeg   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Negated Infinitive
 +IteCau    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Iterative (morphologically: Causative)

!! ### Verb person-numerus
 +1Sg   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 1.person singular
 +2Sg   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 2.person singular
 +3Sg   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 3.person singular
 +4Sg   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 4.person singular
 +1Pl   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 1.person plural
 +2Pl   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 2.person plural
 +3Pl   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 3.person plural
 +4Pl   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 4.person plural
 +1Du   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Subject 1.person dual

 +1SgO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 1.person singular
 +2SgO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 2.person singular
 +3SgO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 3.person singular
 +4SgO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 4.person singular
 +1PlO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 1.person plural
 +2PlO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 2.person plural
 +3PlO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 3.person plural
 +4PlO  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Object 4.person plural

!! ### Possesive tags - Possessormarkering i possessum
 +1SgPoss   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Possessor 1.person singular
